Author: babyfaced-bitch
Text: Update: I forgot I posted this (because I posted right after waking up) and now that I saw it again, I remembered how good it felt to see myself and think I was pretty and now I’m really sad because I saw myself in the mirror before I weighed myself a couple minutes ago and I, in fact, did NOT see the pretty girl that dream-me saw in the mirror so....yeah I’m really sad
